```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "script_purpose": "Runs Keras time tests for different image recognition networks using SLURM job scheduler and MPI for distributed processing.",
    "networks": [
      "AlexNet",
      "InceptionV3",
      "ResNet50",
      "GoogLeNet"
    ],
    "training_parameters": {
      "batch_size": "dynamically calculated based on number of nodes",
      "iterations": 500
    },
    "dependencies": [
      "Python",
      "Keras",
      "MPI",
      "SLURM",
      "PNETCDF",
      "FAKE_SYSTEM_LIBS"
    ],
    "execution_environment": {
      "nodes": "dynamically determined",
      "library_paths": [
        "$PNETCDF_INSTALL_DIR/lib",
        "$FAKE_SYSTEM_LIBS/lib",
        "$FAKE_SYSTEM_LIBS/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu",
        "$FAKE_SYSTEM_LIBS/usr/lib64/gconv",
        "$FAKE_SYSTEM_LIBS/usr/lib64/audit",
        "$LD_LIBRARY_PATH"
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
